In re Resignation of Johnson.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Johnson (1991), 59 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. 91-549 Submitted March 20, 1991 Decided March 27, 1991.)

The resignation of Charles W. Johnson as an attorney is accepted; he must surrender his Certificate of Admission to the practice of law.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur,
